{"type": "article", "id": 2822, "title": "飞镖状瓶塞小工具", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-14T09:30:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232233SwmJGsiCoNX5hr6F.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如果你正在为还未喝完的红酒如何保存发愁的话，韩国设计品牌 Connect Design 带来的这款名为“ Torpedo ”的小工具或许可以帮到你。Torpedo 形似一个小飞镖，既可以充当红酒酒瓶瓶塞的功能，防止液体挥发，另一边的三个镖翼部分还可以帮助酒瓶更加稳当地存放，不管是倒立或是平放都没有问题。定价 13 美元，<a href=\"http://connectdesign.co.kr/front/php/product.php?product_no=619\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232231CkRynd9IgsSQ0O8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232231OtJMrnWfRXhwbPco.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232232ZJb3LSpUPQHindBw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232232voDMhHzXbaeEFy85.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}